&lt;p&gt;The Silverrudder is a solo regatta where participants sail around the Danish island of Funen. It starts and finishes in Svendborg. It&amp;rsquo;s considered the largest solo regatta in the world and sells out quickly every year. The regatta attracts a wide variety of boats, from small monohulls and multihulls to larger vessels.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Position</title><link>https://lucy.hamburg/position/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://lucy.hamburg/position/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Lucy's last recorded position:
